{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-movement-using-css-animation","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Napravi kretanje koristeci CSS animaciju","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada elementi imaju definisan <code>position</code>, kao sto su <code>fixed</code> ili <code>relative</code>, CSS offset svojstva <code>right</code>, <code>left</code>, <code>top</code> i <code>bottom</code> mogu da se koriste u pravilima animacije za kreiranje kretanja.</p>\n<p>Kao sto je prikazano u primeru ispod, element mozete pomeriti nadole pa nagore tako sto postavite <code>top</code> svojstvo keyframe-a na <code>50%</code> na 50px, dok ostaje 0px u prvom (<code>0%</code>) i poslednjem (<code>100%</code>) frejmu.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">@keyframes rainbow {\n  0% {\n    background-color: blue;\n    top: 0px;\n  }\n  50% {\n    background-color: green;\n    top: 50px;\n  }\n  100% {\n    background-color: yellow;\n    top: 0px;\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"587d78a7367417b2b2512ae1","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodajte horizontalno kretanje <code>div</code> animaciji. Koristeci <code>left</code> offset svojstvo, dopunite <code>@keyframes</code> pravilo tako da rainbow pocinje na 0 piksela u <code>0%</code>, ide na 25 piksela u <code>50%</code> i zavrsava na -25 piksela u <code>100%</code>. Ne menjajte <code>top</code> svojstvo u editoru, animacija treba da ima i vertikalno i horizontalno kretanje.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/c7amZfW","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301051,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-movement-using-css-animation"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  div {\n    height: 40px;\n    width: 70%;\n    background: black;\n    margin: 50px auto;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n\n  #rect {\n    animation-name: rainbow;\n    animation-duration: 4s;\n  }\n\n  @keyframes rainbow {\n    0% {\n      background-color: blue;\n      top: 0px;\n\n    }\n    50% {\n      background-color: green;\n      top: 50px;\n\n    }\n    100% {\n      background-color: yellow;\n      top: 0px;\n\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div id=\"rect\"></div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>@keyframes</code> pravilo za <code>0%</code> treba da koristi <code>left</code> offset od 0px.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/[^50]0%\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*?left:\\s*?0px(;[\\s\\S]*?|\\s*?)}/gi);"},{"text":"<p><code>@keyframes</code> pravilo za <code>50%</code> treba da koristi <code>left</code> offset od 25px.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/50%\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*?left:\\s*?25px(;[\\s\\S]*?|\\s*?)}/gi);"},{"text":"<p><code>@keyframes</code> pravilo za <code>100%</code> treba da koristi <code>left</code> offset od -25px.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/100%\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*?left:\\s*?-25px(;[\\s\\S]*?|\\s*?)}/gi);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"create-movement-using-css-animation","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"applied-visual-design","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-visual-direction-by-fading-an-element-from-left-to-right","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/modify-fill-mode-of-an-animation","id":"587d78a7367417b2b2512ae1","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-timing-function: linear;\n  }\n  #blue {\n    background: blue;\n    left: 50%;\n    animation-timing-function: ease-out;\n  }\n  #green {\n    background: green;\n    left: 75%;\n    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.311, 0.441, 0.444, 1.649);\n  }\n\n  @keyframes jump {\n    50% {\n      top: 10%;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"red\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"blue\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"green\"></div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-movement-using-css-animation"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}